Type: Package
Package: mwbenchr
Title: R Interface to Metabolomics Workbench REST API
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2025-08-29
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive R interface to the Metabolomics
    Workbench REST API (v1.2). The package enables programmatic access to
    metabolomics data, compound information, study metadata, and
    analytical tools. It supports all major API contexts including study,
    compound, RefMet, MetStat, and mass spectrometry data retrieval with
    built-in caching and error handling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/danymukesha/mwbenchr, 
    https://danymukesha.github.io/mwbenchr
